msgid "Discover more of your journey - Powered by the community"
msgstr "Trovya moy a dha kerdh - Selys war'n gemeneth"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra freedom description
#: content/_index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Discover your journey, navigate the world with privacy and community at the forefront."
msgstr "Trovya dha kerdh, viajya an nor gans privetter ha kemeneth a-rag."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra freedom title
#: content/_index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Freedom Is Here"
msgstr "Rydhses Yw Omma"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra map description
#: content/_index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Community + Open Maps"
msgstr "Kemeneth + Mappys Rydh"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra services items description
#: content/_index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Plan and navigate your trip abroad with just GPS, no need for mobile data. Search waypoints while on distant hiking trails or bike paths."
msgstr "Devisya ha viajya dha viaj tramor gans GPS hepken, nyns eus res rag data gwayadow. Hwilas leow ha war lerghow gwandrans pell po hensyow diwros."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra services items highlight text
#: content/_index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "No internet needed"
msgstr "Ny res kesrosweyth vyth"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra services items title
#: content/_index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Offline Search and Route"
msgstr "Hwithrans Dhywarlinen ha Navigacyon"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra services items description
#: content/_index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "The app is designed with privacy in mind - does not identify people, does not track you, and does not collect any information. CoMaps was also audited by <span class=\"text-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 19 19\"><use href=\"#icon-exodus\"></use></svg> [Exodus](https://reports.exodus-privacy.eu.org/reports/app.comaps.google/latest/)."
msgstr "An app yw desinys gans privetter yn brys - ny aswon tus, ny helerghi tus, ha ny kuntel neb kedhlow. Ynwedh, CoMaps yw arhwilys gans <span class=\"text-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 19 19\"><use href=\"#icon-exodus\"></use></svg> [Exodus](https://reports.exodus-privacy.eu.org/reports/app.comaps.google/latest/)."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra services items highlight text
#: content/_index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Privacy by default"
msgstr "Privetter yn Defowt"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra services items title
#: content/_index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "No Data Collection"
msgstr "Kuntel Data Vyth"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra services items description
#: content/_index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Efficiently uses the battery, doesn’t drain your battery like other navigation apps."
msgstr "Devnydhya yn effeythadow an batri, ny gwakhe dha batri avel appys navigacyon aral."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra services items highlight text
#: content/_index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Efficient battery use"
msgstr "Devnydh effeythadow batri"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra services items title
#: content/_index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Save Your Battery"
msgstr "Sawya Dha Batri"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra services items description
#: content/_index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "People like you are helping build the app by adding locations to <span class=\"text-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 19 19\"><use href=\"#icon-open-street-map\"></use></svg> [OpenStreetMap](https://openstreetmap.org)</span>, giving feedback on features, and contributing code on <span class=\"text-icon\"><svg viewbox=\"0 0 4.233 4.233\"> <use href=\"#icon-codeberg\"></use></svg> [Codeberg](https://codeberg.org/comaps)</span> to create great maps together. The project is a fork of Organic Maps and Maps.Me, and driven by an open-source community."
msgstr "Tus kepar ha ty ow gweres byldya an app gans ow keworra tylleryow dhe <span class=\"text-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 19 19\"><use href=\"#icon-open-street-map\"></use></svg>[OpenStreetMap](https://openstreetmap.org)</span>, ow tasliva war nasyow, hag ow kevri kod war <span class=\"text-icon\"><svg viewbox=\"0 0 4.233 4.233\"><use href=\"#icon-codeberg\"></use></svg>[Codeberg](https://codeberg.org/comaps)</span> rag gul mappys bryntin war-barth. An ragdes yw forgh a Organic Maps ha Maps.Me, ha selys war gemeneth rydh."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra services items highlight text
#: content/_index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Free for everyone, Made with love"
msgstr "Rydh rag onan hag oll, Gwrys gans kerensa"

