#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra funding items text
#: content/donate/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Currently there is no full time team who is working to develop new features and improve the service. To consistently move the product forward, a core team is needed."
msgstr "Y'n eur ma, nyns eus bagas pes neb a ow lavurya rag gul nasyow nowydh ha gwellhe an gonis. Rag ragwaya yn kesson, bagas kresel yw res."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra funding items title
#: content/donate/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Developers"
msgstr "Awtours"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra funding items text
#: content/donate/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "We have to keep up fast servers, so anyone in the world can download free map data updates without delays. These maps data transfers make up large, and growing, amounts of data each month."
msgstr "Res yw dhyn gwitha servellow uskis, rag may nebonan war'n nor a yll iskarga nowedhyansow mappys rydh heb lettys. An dreusporthow data mappys ma moghhe pub mis."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra funding items title
#: content/donate/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Infrastructure"
msgstr "Isframweyth"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra funding items text
#: content/donate/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "User support, fixing bugs, and improving the stability of the app are our top priority. The list of requests and bug reports grows every day, and there are many support requests to respond to on the App Store, Google Play, and support emails."
msgstr "Skoodhyans devnydhyoryon, owth ewnhe kudynnow, ha gwellhe an faster app yw agan ragwiryow. An rol a wovynnow ha derivasow kudynnow moghhe pub dydh, hag yma meur a wovynnow skoodhyans rag gorthebi dhe war'n App Store, Google Play, hag ebostow skoodhyans."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/donate/index.md content/support/_index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Support"
msgstr "Skoodhyans"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra funding title
#: content/donate/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "How will funding be used?"
msgstr "Fatel wren arghasans devnydhys?"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra info text
#: content/donate/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "We rely on your donations to keep CoMaps open and free"
msgstr "Ni fydhya war dha argevrohow rag gwitha CoMaps ygor ha rydh"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra info text
#: content/donate/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "We are a few enthusiasts contributing in our free time. We love what we do, and we love our users"
msgstr "Nebes tus dhiwysyk on ow kevri yn agan termyn rydh. Ni kara an pyth a wren ni, ha ni kara agan devnydhyoryon"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra info text
#: content/donate/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "With your support, we are working toward privacy-focused map navigation that is the preferred choice on the market"
msgstr "Gans dha skoodhyans, on ow lavurya troha navigacyon privedh yw an dewis dewisek war'n varghas"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: description
#: content/support/_index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Need assistance? Search for answers to common questions. Get the support you need and connect with others in the community for help."
msgstr "Eus edhom dhywgh a weres? Hwilas rag gorthebow dhe wovynnow kemmyn. Kavos an gweres ty res hag omjunya gans re erel y'n gemeneth rag gweres."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: description
#: content/about-us/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Free and open navigation with privacy -<br/>Built by the community"
msgstr "Navigacyon rydh hag ygor gans privetter -<br/>Byldya gans an gemeneth"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra about text
#: content/about-us/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "CoMaps is a community-focused privacy navigation app for travelers - drivers, hikers, and cyclists. It uses the crowd-sourced OpenStreetMap data with contributors from all over the globe. It offers navigation with privacy - no identifying people and no data collection. CoMaps features can operate without an active internet connection for offline navigation at urban or distant locations, where cellular service is not available. CoMaps is an open-source project, and prioritizes community development."
msgstr "CoMaps yw app navigacyon fogellys war gemeneth rag tremenysi - lewyoryon, kerdhoryon, ha diwrosyoryon. Ow tevnydhya an data routh-gwrys OpenStreetMap gans kevriysi dres oll an bys tw. Owth offra navigacyon gans privetter yw - owth aswon tus vyth ha kuntel data vyth. Nasyow CoMaps a yll oberi heb junyans kesrosweyth byw rag navigation dhywarlinen yn tylleryow trevel po pell, le may gonis klapkodh yw ankavadow. CoMaps yw ragdres rydh, ha ragwirhe displegyans kemeneth."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra about title
#: content/about-us/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Free and open navigation with privacy, built by the community"
msgstr "Navigacyon rydh hag ygor gans privetter, byldys gans an gemeneth"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra history items text
#: content/about-us/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "MapsWithMe navigation app created (later renamed to Maps.me)."
msgstr "App navigacyon MapsWithMe gwrys (dashenwelys diwettha dhe Vaps.me)."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra history items text
#: content/about-us/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Maps.me opened the source code under Apache 2.0 license."
msgstr "Maps.me ygerys an kod yn leshyans Apache 2.0."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra history items text
#: content/about-us/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "The Organic Maps project & company were founded, based on the Maps.Me source code."
msgstr "An ragdres ha kompani Organic Maps o selys, selys war'n kod Maps.Me."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra history items text
#: content/about-us/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Governance issues and community concerns not addressed by company shareholders stalled the development of Organic Maps for months."
msgstr "Kudynnow governieth ha bernyow kemeneth ny kewsel orth gans kevranoryon hedhys an displegyans dres misyow."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra history items text
#: content/about-us/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "The **CoMaps** community & non-profit project was founded by former Organic Maps contributors, based on the Organic Maps source code."
msgstr "An gemeneth **CoMaps** & ragdres heb budh o selys gans kevrisi kyns Organic Maps, selys war'n kod Organic Maps."

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra history title
#: content/about-us/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "History"
msgstr "Istori"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: extra vm items text
#: content/about-us/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Unlock the freedom to easily navigate offline, with privacy-focused maps for drivers, hikers, and cyclists, powered by the community."
msgstr "Dialhwedha an rydhses rag viajya dhywarlinen yn es, gans mappys privedh rag lewyoryon, kerdhoryon, ha diwrosyoryon, selys war'n gemeneth."

